n features to easily create, edit and manage content for websites. Keep your site under control with a powerful backend web administration panel. PHPFusion comes in 2 version, one lightweight and the other a full-suite with latest feature implementations for your choosing. </p> </div> <div class="start-grid"> <div class="item"> <span>1 Solution Suite</span> </div> <div class="item"> <span>Modular custom design</span> </div> <div class="item"> <span>SEO friendly</span> </div> <div class="item"> <span>Responsive design</span> </div> <div class="item"> <span>Modular system</span> </div> <div class="item"> <span>Fast performant</span> </div> <div class="item"> <span>Security</span> </div> <div class="item"> <span>Multi-language</span> </div> </div> </div> <div class="start-bg"> <div class="start-bg1 orb"></div> <div class="start-bg2 orb"></div> <div class="start-bg3 orb"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!---//marketplace-hero---> <div class="mp-hero hero-section"> <div class="mp-hero-block stackdown"> <div class="mp-content-hero"> <h5>Marketplace</h5> <h3>Expand with the best ADDONS & THEMES with Marketplace</h3> <p>The Marketplace can prepare you for your website needs. When you need help with them, you can check out our community forum.</p> </div> <div class="mp-content-meta"> <div id="mpTypesSlide" class="splide" aria-label="Marketplace Types"> <div class="splide__track"> <div class="splide__list"> <a href="#" class="mp-types splide__slide"> <div class="list-group-item"> <h4> <span class="icon"><img src="themes/FusionTheme/images/icons/infusion.svg" alt="Infusion" loading="lazy"></span>Infusion </h4> <p>These addons to expands the functionality and features of your website with just a simple install</p> </div> </a> <a href="#" class="mp-types splide__slide"> <div class="list-group-item"> <h4> <span class="icon"><img src="themes/FusionTheme/images/icons/theme.svg" alt="Theme" loading="lazy"></span> Themes </h4> <p>Discover more themes and templates that can change 